race.description: Kevin Sharkie Tasmanian Oaks 20 Feb Maiden Plate
race.comment: MONCLERE (4) was quickly back on track beaten 1L this track and trip. Is running out of chances but he's on a quick backup with Newitt engaged for the first time. Rates best and will be flashing late. SEDITIOUS AWARD (12) finished 1.3 lengths from the winner over 1600m at Hobart and had been within range the two prior over 1400m. The claim is handy and he can go top-three this time. SH'BOURNE RISING (13) was tracking well on turf before a flop on the synthetic at a short quote when he resented the kickback. The 2kg claim helps but the barrier is awkward. NATALDI (14) is on a quick backup and has the blinkers on for the first time. He showed enough three back on debut to suggest she'll win some races.
